Testing all in 1 machine
--------------------------
java user alice localhost 1067 amazon
java broker 1067 localhost 1068
java ecommerce amazon 1068

Testing each in a different machine
Alice : IP1
Broker: IP2 Port2
Amazon  :  IP3 Port3
java user alice ip2 port2 amazon
java broker port2 ip3 port3
java ecommerce amazon port3

Sample netmachine configs
Alice: net01
Broker: net02 1067
Amazon: net03 1068
java user alice net02.utdallas.edu 1067 amazon
java broker 1067 net03.utdallas.edu 1068
java ecommerce amazon 1068